//! ActivityPub Object representation for **{{ model }}**.
//!
//! Follows the architecture of [`activitypub-federation-rust`]:
//! - [`Apub{{ model }}`] is the serialisable AP JSON-LD representation.
//! - [`Db{{ model }}`] wraps the SeaORM [`Model`] with a resolved `ap_id` URL.
//! - Conversion between DB model ↔ AP JSON is handled via dedicated methods
//!   mirroring the `Object` trait pattern (`into_json` / `from_json`).
//! - Activities (`Create`, `Update`, `Delete`) wrap the object following the
//!   `Activity` trait pattern.

